Basics.image2image: Transform existing images using text prompts.

Flux.flux_redux_model_example: Transfer style from a reference image to guide image generation with Flux.

Image.hidream_i1_dev: Generate images with HiDream I1 Dev.
Image.hidream_i1_fast: Generate images quickly with HiDream I1.

Image.sd3_5_large_blur: Generate images from blurred reference images with SD 3.5.

Image.sdxlturbo_example: Generate images in a single step with SDXL Turbo.

Video.text_to_video_wan: Quickly Generate videos from text descriptions.
Video.wan2_1_fun_inp: Create videos from start and end frames.

Video.wan2_1_flf2v_720_f16: Generate video through controlling the first and last frames.
Video.txt_to_image_to_video: Generate images from text and then convert them into videos.

Image API.api_openai_image_1_t2i: Use GPT Image 1 API to generate images from text descriptions.
Image API.api_openai_image_1_i2i: Use GPT Image 1 API to generate images from images.
Image API.api_openai_image_1_inpaint: Use GPT Image 1 API to inpaint images.
Image API.api_openai_image_1_multi_inputs: Use GPT Image 1 API with multiple inputs to generate images.
Image API.api-openai-dall-e-2-t2i: Use Dall-E 2 API to generate images from text descriptions.
Image API.api-openai-dall-e-2-inpaint: Use Dall-E 2 API to inpaint images.
Image API.api-openai-dall-e-3-t2i: Use Dall-E 3 API to generate images from text descriptions.
Image API.api_bfl_flux_pro_t2i: Create images with FLUX.1 [pro]'s excellent prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity.
Image API.api_stability_sd3_t2i: Generate high quality images with excellent prompt adherence. Perfect for professional use cases at 1 megapixel resolution.
Image API.api_ideogram_v3_t2i: Generate images with high-quality image-prompt alignment, photorealism, and text rendering. Create professional-quality logos, promotional posters, landing page concepts, product photography, and more. Effortlessly craft sophisticated spatial compositions with intricate backgrounds, precise and nuanced lighting and colors, and lifelike environmental detail.
Image API.api_luma_photon_i2i: Guide image generation using a combination of images and prompt.
Image API.api_luma_photon_style_ref: Apply and blend style references with exact control. Luma Photon captures the essence of each reference image, letting you combine distinct visual elements while maintaining professional quality.
Image API.api_recraft_image_gen_with_color_control: Create a custom palette to reuse for multiple images or hand-pick colors for each photo. Match your brand's color palette and craft visuals that are distinctly yours.
Image API.api_recraft_image_gen_with_style_control: Control style with visual examples, align positioning, and fine-tune objects. Store and share styles for perfect brand consistency.
Image API.api_recraft_vector_gen: Go from a text prompt to vector image with Recraft's AI vector generator. Produce the best-quality vector art for logos, posters, icon sets, ads, banners and mockups. Perfect your designs with sharp, high-quality SVG files. Create branded vector illustrations for your app or website in seconds.

Video API.api_luma_i2v: Take static images and instantly create magical high quality animations.
Video API.api_kling_i2v: Create videos with great prompt adherence for actions, expressions, and camera movements. Now supporting complex prompts with sequential actions for you to be the director of your scene.
Video API.api_veo2_i2v: Use Google Veo2 API to generate videos from images.
Video API.api_hailuo_minimax_i2v: Create refined videos from images and text, including CGI integration and trendy photo effects like viral AI hugging. Choose from a variety of video styles and themes to match your creative vision.
Video API.api_pika_scene: Use multiple images as ingredients and generate videos that incorporate all of them.
Video API.api_pixverse_template_i2v: Transforms static images into dynamic videos with motion and effects.
Video API.api_pixverse_t2v: Generate videos with accurate prompt interpretation and stunning video dynamics.
